Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.42,八犬-OP.JP,,0,0,0,,手を伸ばすよ　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:48.00,八犬-OP.JP,,0,0,0,,This heart was asking
